===Noun===
'''policy'''  (''plural:'' [[policies]])
{{wikipedia}}
#a [[plan]] or [[course]] of [[action]], especially one of a [[political]] [[party]] or [[government]]
#* The Communist Party has a '''policy''' of returning power to the workers
#a course of action thought to be [[prudent]] or [[advantageous]]; hence [[prudence]] or [[sagacity]]
#* Honesty is the best '''policy'''
#a [[written]] [[contract]] or [[certificate]] of [[insurance]]
#* You are still insured, even though the '''policy''' was destroyed in the fire

